=head1 NAME

Foorum - Foorum is a forum script built in Catalyst.

=head2 INSTALL

Read INSTALL file at the same dir.

=head2 RUN

you can run it under mod_perl or fastcgi

for test using, we recommend to use builtin server.pl try:
  
  perl bin/foorum_server.pl -k

=head2 SEE ALSO

L<Catalyst>, L<DBIx::Class>, L<Template>

More at docs/*.html
